description: A handsome, corner 2bed/2bath condo situated in an elegant 19th Century brick, elevator building with 2 car garage parking! In the heart of South Boston, this boutique elevator building was fully restored and renovated into 24 luxury condos in 2014. This 3rd floor corner unit features an ideal open floor plan with chef's kitchen with Wolf range and stainless steel appliances. The home was custom designed by a local craftsman showcasing intricate details throughout- custom wainscoting, chair rails, crown moldings, built-in shelving, surround sound in every room, and custom designed closets. Both queen-sized bedrooms have built-out closets, loads of natural light and are separated by the living room. Gleaming hardwood floors, in-unit laundry, surround sound and central AC round out the unit but the value does not stop there! With a professionally managed building you also get heated two car hydraulic lift garage parking! A quarter mile to the beach, boutique shopping and fine dining!
